Introduction

The document describes step by step instructions for assembling the project eXo IDE (version 1.2.x).
Requirements

    JDK 1.6 or higher
    Maven 2.2.1 (or upper),
    Console SVN client.

Compilation eXo IDE:

1. For the source eXo IDE to the folder ide execute the command

svn co http://svn.exoplatform.org/projects/ide/trunk ide

2. In folder ide execute command:

mvn clean install

3. For assembly IDE with tomcat go to folder exo-ide-packaging-standalone-tomcat execute command:

   mvn clean install -Pmysql    - build package for eXo IDE demo site with MySql
   mvn clean install            - build packaging for eXo IDE demo site with HSQL
   mvn clean install -Pselenium - build package for QA team

4. The address of  deployed IDE is http://localhost:8080/
